### EduPortal API - Reports Controller
### Report generation endpoints (Not fully implemented)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/reports
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET STUDENT PROGRESS REPORT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET STUDENT ACADEMIC REPORT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/academic
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET STUDENT ATTENDANCE REPORT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET COURSE PERFORMANCE REPORT - (Admin, Öğretmen, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/course/1/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET FINANCIAL REPORT - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/financial?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET TEACHER PERFORMANCE REPORT - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/teacher/1/performance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ENROLLMENT REPORT - (Admin, Kayıtçı)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollment?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### EXPORT REPORT TO PDF
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/export/pdf
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reportType": "StudentProgress",
  "studentId": 1,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31"
}

### ===========================================
### EXPORT REPORT TO EXCEL
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/export/excel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reportType": "Financial",
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31"
}
